@apiUrl = https://fw-teaching.fi/demo/wdbocms/api/v1/products/

### Get all products
GET {{apiUrl}}

### Get one product
GET {{apiUrl}}/1002


### Create new product
POST {{apiUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"name": "Jeans",
"price": 49.99
}

### Delete product
DELETE  {{apiUrl}}/1004

### Update product info
PATCH  {{apiUrl}}/1004

{
    "price": 39.99
}